Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
report_cell_edge_spacing(25.10)                report_cell_edge_spacing(25.10)

Name
       report_cell_edge_spacing  -  Reports all the cell edge spacing rules in
       both terminal and log file

Syntax
       report_cell_edge_spacing

       [-help]

       [-file <fileName>]

       Reports all the cell edge spacing rules in both terminal and log file.

Parameters
       -file <fileName>
              Specifies the file name to dump cell edge spacing rules.

       -help  Outputs a brief description that includes the type  and  default
              information for each report_cell_edge_spacing parameter.

              For a detailed description of the command and all of its parame-
              ters, use the man command:

              man report_cell_edge_spacing

Related Information
              * specifyCellEdgeSpacing

              * deleteCellEdgeSpacing

